debug.temperatureTip: Control the randomness of generated text. This parameter can control the diversity of generated text to avoid generating overly similar text.
debug.topPTip: Control the probability threshold for generating text. This parameter can control the diversity of generated text to avoid generating overly similar text.
debug.maxTokensTip: Control the maximum length of generated text. This parameter can control the length of the generated text to avoid generating excessively long text.
debug.topKTip: Control the large model to randomly select a word from the top k words with the highest probability during each word generation, in order to improve the diversity of the generated results while ensuring text coherence.
debug.presencePenaltyTip: Control the existence penalty of generated text. This parameter can control the number of words and phrases that do not exist in the generated text to avoid generating overly disjointed text.
debug.frequencyPenaltyTip: Control the frequency penalty for generating text. This parameter can control the number of repeated words and phrases in the generated text to avoid generating overly repetitive text.
debug.pleaseFillAttachmentURL: Please fill in the attachment URL
debug.clickOrDrag: Click or drag the file here to upload
debug.fillVariable: Fill in the value of the variable, which will be automatically replaced in the prompt words every time the question is submitted
debug.uploadFailedPleaseTryAgain: File upload failed, please try again
debug.cannotExceed5: The number of files cannot exceed 5
debug.cannotBothVideosAndImages: Files cannot upload both videos and images simultaneously
debug.singleFileCannotThan50M: A single file cannot be larger than 50M
debug.videosCannotExceedOne: The number of videos cannot exceed one
